snippet.textDisplay:
Everything that works about this video:
-the dynamics between Noel’s low vocal register and Cody’s high-soft register makes every transition between verse and chorus interesting and appealing to the ear
-the use of bold colors and spacing make every second of the video visually appealing
-the chorus is soooo strong and the change in the lyrical ride of the rhythm between chorus and verse is extremely engaging
-the comedy is there but it isn’t the focus
-Cody found his niche with his vocals in this song and I hope it continues on

What doesn’t work about this video:
-effectively having and ad as long as the song that’s featured (totally understandable to have an ad in the video though, so it gets a pass)
-not a whole lot else honestly
